<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-12191] Bzip2Factory is not thread safe</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-12191</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Bzip2Factory.isNativeBzip2Loaded is not protected from multiple threads calling it simultaneously.  A thread can return false from this method despite logging the fact that was going to return true due to manipulations of the static boolean from another thread calling the same method.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
